!! IMPORTANT !!

For best results:

Use CFG 6 or below. I've seen good results all the way down to CFG 2.

Use a non-latent HiRes upscaler such as 4x-Ultrasharp or Foolhardy-Remacri at a low denoising level between 0.25-0.3.

Use a low denoising level when using Img2Img also.
